title: Temple of the Undead Magus
story: For many years the temple of the Undead Magus was considered lost. These days it is infested by boars, indifferent to the past of the place. The temple of the Undead Magus is home to a rare specie of mushrooms.

notes.text: A fresco on the wall depicting the land around the temple.
A large stone door with a keyhole on the eastern wall.
A leather armor among rubble on the ground.
A jellyfied body of a bandit, a key close to it.
A smith, sleeping in a corner.
